metadata.description:
Canada's legendary artist has been trailblazing the scene and is now dropping his Genesis NFT! 

This NFT consists of the original cover art from his mixtape series 'Don't Sleep'.  

As a classic from his catalogue, his fans and supporters have been following him in cult fashion since the mixtape dropped in 2012. Now you can own a piece of Toronto rap history and support one of Canada's leading rappers. 

Included:

  • Roney Album art - Don't Sleep
  • Roney Custom art (one-of-a-kind unique ownership)
  • Roney 'deletevideo'
  • PDF unlockable

Purchasing this NFT will also unlock a 15-minute live video call with RONEY!

Background on the artist: 

Roney is one of the most consistent artists in Toronto and all of Canada. 

Roney is known for his massive 2020 singles such as 'Go There' which amassed over 1 million YouTube streams and 2 million Spotify streams in just 8 months. He’s made the cover of “Northern Bars” a Spotify editorial playlist several times and his music added to major editorial playlists such as; Hip Hop Central, Hip Hop Favourites and New Music Friday Canada.

He continuously releases new singles, videos and remixes; his work-ethic is unmatched. His catalogue is impressive and still growing.

*The live 15-minute video call with Roney will not be included with any secondary sales*
